### macOS / Linux
```bash
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
./bilsim
```

### Windows (Visual Studio)
```bash
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
cmake --build . --config Release
.\Release\bilsim.exe
```

## Controls
- **W / UP Arrow** - Accelerate forward
- **S / DOWN Arrow** - Accelerate backward
- **A / LEFT Arrow** - Turn left
- **D / RIGHT Arrow** - Turn right

## Adding Engine Sound
Place an engine sound file (WAV, MP3, or OGG) at:
```
assets/sounds/engine.wav
```

If no sound file is found, the simulator will run without audio.

## Project Structure
```
src/
  audio/       - Sound management (irrKlang)
  core/        - Vehicle physics (backend)
  graphics/    - 3D rendering (frontend)
  input/       - Keyboard handling
  ui/          - User interface
```

## Dependencies
- **threepp** - 3D graphics library (auto-downloaded)
- **irrKlang** - Audio library (auto-downloaded)

